</div>    

<div class="level4">
 <span class="level5"><a href="<?php echo $mainscpage; ?>/?q=bu-pm#pli-tv-bu-pm:12.0">Pārājika 4. Uttarimanussadhamma</a> <a href="<?php echo $mainscpage; ?>/?q=bu-pj4#pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:2.12.1">vb</a> Yo pana bhikkhu anabhijānaṁ uttarimanussadhammaṁ attupanāyikaṁ alamariyañāṇadassanaṁ samudācareyya “iti jānāmi, iti passāmī”ti,
