<a href="<?php echo $mainscpage; ?>/?q=pli-tv-bu-vb-ss4#pli-tv-bu-vb-ss4:1.2.19.0">vb</a> Yo pana bhikkhu otiṇṇo vipariṇatena cittena mātugāmassa santike attakāmapāricariyāya vaṇṇaṁ bhāseyya “etadaggaṁ bhagini pāricariyānaṁ yā mādisaṁ sīlavantaṁ kalyāṇadhammaṁ brahmacāriṁ etena dhammena paricareyyā”ti methunupasaṁhitena, saṅghādiseso.
